Title: No One to Watch Over Me
Plot: Allison has recurring dreams of her being out in the snow, where she eventually finds a young woman's body.  Joe meanwhile returns to work for the first time since the shooting, still trying to deal with the repercussions of the tragedy.
GuestStars: James Chiareillo, Kate McGregor-Stewart, Elisabeth Moss, Gerry Becker, Ruben Garfias, Adrian Sparks, Kimberly Scott, Robert Neary, Kerris Lilla Dorsey
